{"tid":1107690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰誤賣一折機票 找數完美拆彈","createTime":"2019-04-15T12:13:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T16:59:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"009e993bb33e8d4e60825070449df61e4dd87891","tid":1107690,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:13:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190415/20656355\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190415%2F20656355&d=hmtFoPnP%2FIv5fOqUL3ZUaiLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=8d97d215\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190415%2F20656355&h=fe625d05\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190415/20656355</a><br />\n<br />\n國泰誤賣一折機票 找數完美拆彈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190415/large/19146082.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190415%2Flarge%2F19146082.jpg&h=cbad0d6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國泰年初由里斯本飛往香港的部份票價離奇「大減價」，惟最終仍承認這批交易，並以「帶着神秘的限時驚喜」打圓場。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】企業「擺烏龍」隨時演變成「關公災難」，國泰航空網上預訂機票系統今年初兩周內兩度出錯，變成「頭等機票大平賣」；正當市場以為國泰會取消交易了事，公關團隊完美「拆彈」。<br />\n<br />\n國泰年初由里斯本飛往香港的部份票價離奇「大減價」，部份更低至1折，國泰航空最終承認這批交易，並以「帶着神秘的限時驚喜」打圓場，說期待在航班上跟各「快閃參加者」見面，又表示「從小就學會錯就要認」，勇敢認錯兼做「找數真漢子」，成功轉化成「關公」宣傳手段。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：東亞擺烏龍 回贈$5,300變53萬 涉多名客戶 律師：動用或犯盜竊罪<br />\n<br />\n豐澤派300元禮券<br />\n<br />\n另一經典例子是豐澤網店擺烏龍，去年12月以298元平賣iPhone、MacBook、智能電視及相機等。網民紛紛搶購並在社交平台大晒「戰利品」照片。豐澤其後解釋網店系統發生故障，導致商品「標錯價」，向受影響人士致歉，指盡快取消交易及安排退款，並會向受影響人士派發300元禮券。<br />\n<br />\n去年3月，港鐵青衣站㩒錯廣播引發恐慌，當時突然響起緊急疏散廣播，乘客慌忙拍卡出閘，惟其後站務員澄清是「㩒錯掣」誤報，港鐵即安排檢查系統，並向被多扣車資者退款。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黃珮琳  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n東亞擺烏龍 回贈$5,300變53萬  涉多名客戶 律師：動用或犯盜竊罪<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n測量師被揭估大面積推高工程費<br />\n<br />\n東亞擺烏龍 回贈$5,300變53萬 涉多名客戶 律師：動用或犯盜竊罪"},{"pid":"805bc4e654e62545fd0c638a1b63dfc7249b7550","tid":1107690,"uid":35430,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:14:51.000Z","msg":"因航經歷過咁多大事，公關經驗方面一般公司邊有得比呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a85e8c20c6b802cc211db46b0de842bbb57f5d0","tid":1107690,"uid":35365,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:17:33.000Z","msg":"因航心諗畀晒你真係一折蝕得去邊<br />\n之前炒油蝕既都唔知幾多倍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ada35c2bb6ee64897389cc6dfcb0a1038e2c70","tid":1107690,"uid":58630,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:24:35.000Z","msg":"炒幾隻it狗咪補返條數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a93250d8eb55404a4e21ad6b5f34b1e4aa46bd","tid":1107690,"uid":59278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:24:58.000Z","msg":"新聞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c3369a0ec93aed08ea74ac8711b5ea18ce9cbd","tid":1107690,"uid":220701,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:00:01.000Z","msg":"某電器鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f704462ae79eb0de136d935b5b7b103c9c392f99","tid":1107690,"uid":5490,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5a85e8c20c6b802cc211db46b0de842bbb57f5d0","tid":1107690,"uid":35365,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:17:33.000Z","msg":"因航心諗畀晒你真係一折蝕得去邊<br />\n之前炒油蝕既都唔知幾多倍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:08:05.000Z","msg":"機票好少錢姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f342815e2653d001d00083a19da98e1c9d178f0d","tid":1107690,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:12:03.000Z","msg":"頭等客豈能得罪<br />\n如果錯價發生喺經濟客位 你估仲會唔會認數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d3999e64b6ae7ac103de0ef7cd2ca86ec67c66","tid":1107690,"uid":24296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:17:41.000Z","msg":"當free upgrade 姐"},{"pid":"c715af7a4ccaaf51d2f524fe7e4f415d218ba97b","tid":1107690,"uid":1845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:31:15.000Z","msg":"班機點都要開 <br />\n多一個客 就係多一筆錢"},{"pid":"2139fdd2fdb90bd66c958a363038c59784a48b77","tid":1107690,"uid":176442,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f342815e2653d001d00083a19da98e1c9d178f0d","tid":1107690,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:12:03.000Z","msg":"頭等客豈能得罪<br />\n如果錯價發生喺經濟客位 你估仲會唔會認數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:55:01.000Z","msg":"戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d1cdc2a557d43392d39c0a05e4c5e6158ece17","tid":1107690,"uid":60665,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T16:07:23.000Z","msg":"晒少少錢但可以轉危為機<br />\n唔晒既話就會係公關災難"},{"pid":"50338ac1f5812cc58b1612a9d79edb28db0db211","tid":1107690,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T16:29:57.000Z","msg":"順手做埋宣傳連廣告都慳埋<br />\n最好出發個日又採訪多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n計落都幾和味"},{"pid":"6d45615ffed20715912b4c06b871656b6053383d","tid":1107690,"uid":122709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T16:37:16.000Z","msg":"數量應該唔係好多，加上頭等就算一折都貴過經濟好多，當豪比佢"},{"pid":"f7af6a529e1b98173449d73cd803cc1891e27491","tid":1107690,"uid":59955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-0